{"data": [{"id": "4741854", "title": "Trump Tailwinds Could Take Altria Group Stock To $100", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"100 years. Happy birthday. Old turtle.\" data-id=\"1295741643\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"983px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">malerapaso</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis Summary</h2> <p><b>Altria Group, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MO\" title=\"Altria Group, Inc.\">MO</a></span>) has had a great year, delivering over 50% returns and outperforming the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SP500</a>).</p> <p>The company has benefitted from the strong adoption of its non-smokable products, and the valuation has expanded.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1295741643/image_1295741643.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741854-trump-tailwinds-could-take-altria-group-stock-to-100", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 23:03:34"}, {"id": "4741848", "title": "FDLO: Balancing Growth And Stability With Low Volatility", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Three Dimensional Graph Of Volatile Data From Sticks And Spheres\" data-id=\"1304192083\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"10000px\" height=\"5000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">peepo</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>ETF Overview</h2> <p>Fidelity Low Volatility Factor ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FDLO\" title=\"Fidelity Low Volatility Factor ETF\">FDLO</a></span>) invests in a portfolio of about 130 low volatility stocks in the United States. The fund tracks the Fidelity U.S. Low Volatility Factor Index. This index basically selects large-cap stocks with lower</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1304192083/image_1304192083.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741848-fdlo-balancing-growth-and-stability-with-low-volatility", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:51:49"}, {"id": "4741847", "title": "Boyd Gaming: I'm Raising My $78 Price Target To $90 On Bullish Signs Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Casino online concept. Betting and gambling online idea. Play poker on internet\" data-id=\"2159323742\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sinenkiy</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h3>Merry Christmas and Happy portfolio New Year</h3> <p>Certainly, holders of <b>Boyd Gaming Corporation</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BYD\" title=\"Boyd Gaming Corporation\">BYD</a></span>) over the last several years have much to celebrate on the performance of the stock. I have been a fan of its management </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159323742/image_2159323742.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741847-boyd-gaming-raising-price-target-on-bullish-signs-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:48:10"}, {"id": "4741843", "title": "Petrodollar Under Threat: Saudi Arabia Wavers While Trump Warns BRICKS", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Petroleum, petrodollar and crude oil concept : Pump jack and China CNY yuan on US USD dollar notes, depicts the money received or earned from sales after investment in the development of oil industry.\" data-id=\"1024533970\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">William_Potter/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>A major geopolitical theme is unfolding, this time directly related to the status of the US Dollar as a global reserve currency. Specifically, according to Reuters, Saudi Arabia \"<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/world/saudi-arabia-abandons-pursuit-us-defence-treaty-over-israel-stalemate-2024-11-29/\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.reuters.com/world/saudi-arabia-abandons-pursuit-us-defence-treaty-over-israel-stalemate-2024-11-29/\" target=\"_blank\">abandons pursuit of US defense treaty over Israel stalemate</a>\".</p> <p>What does this</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1024533970/image_1024533970.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741843-petrodollar-under-threat-saudi-arabia-wavers-while-trump-warns-bricks", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:45:14"}, {"id": "4741841", "title": "H World Group: Demand And Supply Environment Remains Very Attractive", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wide shot hotel manager helping businessman at hotel front desk\" data-id=\"1847793803\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Summary</h2> <p>I gave a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4718515-h-world-group-earnings-robust-domestic-travel-leisure-demand-outlook\">buy rating</a> to H World Group (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HTHT\" title=\"H World Group Limited\">HTHT</a></span>) in September, with my key thesis being that domestic travel in China remains robust and HTHT is in a great position to capture this demand. I</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1847793803/image_1847793803.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741841-h-world-group-demand-and-supply-environment-remains-very-attractive", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:36:50"}, {"id": "4741839", "title": "Cloudflare Shows That It Is '2021' All Over Again", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Social networking service. Streaming video. communication network. 3D illustration.\" data-id=\"1312417734\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3840px\" height=\"2160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">metamorworks</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Cloudflare (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NET\" title=\"Cloudflare, Inc.\">NET</a></span>) has been one of the stronger performers in an already-hot tech sector. The company is showing signs that an inflection in growth rates is coming ahead, which appears to have turbo-charged shares higher. But one could argue that valuations have</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1312417734/image_1312417734.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741839-cloudflare-shows-that-it-is-2021-all-over-again", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:34:37"}, {"id": "4741838", "title": "Trump And The Stock Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Wall Street sign post with American national flags in background. New York city financial district, stock market trade and exchange, or business concept\" data-id=\"1143075035\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5649px\" height=\"3767px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sushiman</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>\"Global investors are committing more capital to a single country than ever before in modern history,\" writes Ruchir Sharma in the <a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/49cca8d7-7b6e-47e3-a50c-9557d7c85fc0\" rel=\"nofollow\">Financial Times</a></p> <p>These investors are \"United by faith in the strength of U.S. financial markets and their capacity to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1143075035/image_1143075035.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741838-trump-and-the-stock-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:26:03"}, {"id": "4741836", "title": "The Two Trillion Dollar Question And The S&P 500's Cautionary Risk Premium", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman Popping The Stock Market Bubble\" data-id=\"1264544465\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"4800px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544465.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1264544465/image_1264544