631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By David Stonberg </em></p> <p>There are attractive opportunities for experienced liquidity providers in the current private equity market environment.</p> <p>Higher capital costs, dampened exit activity and protracted fundraising cycles have presented private equity (PE) sponsors with a fundamental dilemma: How to balance</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1688772631/image_1688772631.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741857-opportunities-across-private-equitys-current-liquidity-landscape", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:19:00"}, {"id": "4741820", "title": "Copa Holdings: The Most Undervalued Airline Stock To Buy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"COPA Airlines Boeing 737 MAX 9\" data-id=\"1928902966\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1021px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/c